<section class="home-page__story" aria-label="Our story">
  <div class="home-page__container">
    <h2 class="home-page__story-title">Our story</h2>
    <div class="home-page__story-content">
      <p>I started Playtime Pets with my wife after being on another big buying and selling platform—however I didn't feel like I was connecting with my customers like I wanted to. In the brick-and-mortar store I have a connection with all the customers, and I wanted that to be the experience people get when they shop online with us.</p>
      <p>I felt I could make the online shopping experience as close as possible to being in the store with me. People have questions, they have concerns, and sometimes there is a problem. When any of these occur, people want someone to answer their questions or address any issues—not ignore them.</p>
      <p>I will always acknowledge your purchase and ship out the next day when possible. We take pride in people having a great experience shopping with us.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

